{"tid":159533,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇VA嘅巴打可以答一答小弟呢個無知嘅問題？","createTime":"2017-03-17T05:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T06:16:09.000Z","uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e75189d94ba3d0c99c81df3f12eb55fe776f414","tid":159533,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一幅畫有幾隻色<br />\n係指佢用咗嘅顏料？溝出嚟嘅唔計？<br />\n啫係我用紅黑+紅溝黑去畫畫<br />\n剩係計紅同黑？<br />\n仲有白色都係唔計？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭先睇畢加索展見到啲number同我數嘅唔同，所以八卦一問<br />\n想sure下正確與否<br />\n所以想八卦一問"},{"pid":"1f48bf1d312247bab07d8ab229b0fdb8209c1d0f","tid":159533,"uid":45635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"睇錯AV 嘅巴打，我都係返出去先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04613922e2e908e1493f774c0e4a0bfa06ec74f","tid":159533,"uid":15900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T05:45:59.000Z","msg":"應該係指原色+溝岀嚟既色<br />\n例如用紅黑，紅+黑會變左暗紅色，如果你幅畫有都會計埋<br />\n黑白色如果係幅畫搵到咪計囉"},{"pid":"7a0979ee853f08bbd0b86ef6ff4aacde458d4560","tid":159533,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:03:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係指原色+溝岀嚟既色<br />\n例如用紅黑，紅+黑會變左暗紅色，如果你幅畫有都會計埋<br />\n黑白色如果係幅畫搵到咪計囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打，但我見畢加索幅畫<br />\n我數到有七隻色<br />\n佢話係五隻色啵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個幅係咩好出名嘅戴帽嘅佢老婆"},{"pid":"b3dad6707a6dca1ac48bf77de7cd22076e1fa134","tid":159533,"uid":15900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:11:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>應該係指原色+溝岀嚟既色<br />\n例如用紅黑，紅+黑會變左暗紅色，如果你幅畫有都會計埋<br />\n黑白色如果係幅畫搵到咪計囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打，但我見畢加索幅畫<br />\n我數到有七隻色<br />\n佢話係五隻色啵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個幅係咩好出名嘅戴帽嘅佢老婆</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪呢個原因，但你試下將一隻色加水，跟住拉一條線，要由佢原本隻色拉到變冇色既漸變<br />\n你會見到中間既淺色係唔同原本隻色，但係同一隻色黎<br />\n唔知係咪因為咁樣"},{"pid":"e933e564957eb260478dafce448c2950b37bb952","tid":159533,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>應該係指原色+溝岀嚟既色<br />\n例如用紅黑，紅+黑會變左暗紅色，如果你幅畫有都會計埋<br />\n黑白色如果係幅畫搵到咪計囉</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打，但我見畢加索幅畫<br />\n我數到有七隻色<br />\n佢話係五隻色啵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個幅係咩好出名嘅戴帽嘅佢老婆</blockquote><br />\n唔知係咪呢個原因，但你試下將一隻色加水，跟住拉一條線，要由佢原本隻色拉到變冇色既漸變<br />\n你會見到中間既淺色係唔同原本隻色，但係同一隻色黎<br />\n唔知係咪因為咁樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 學到嘢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/141427_476858353a9309fac6bfff7de81c83d4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F141427_476858353a9309fac6bfff7de81c83d4.jpg&h=86815412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網搵返原來係我錯<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頭先現場睇有個位係黃色.....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知我盲撚咗定點...."},{"pid":"d0f29f8a56901fc931b80bb3984ba243d9c1ebe3","tid":159533,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"Btw thx bro"}]}